  "keyFeatures": [
    "Highly customizable particle animations using a simple JSON configuration",
    "Confetti and fireworks effects with zero dependencies",
    "Official framework components for React, Vue 2/3, Angular, Svelte, and more",
    "Plugin system for custom shapes, paths, interactions, and effects",
    "CDN-ready bundles (basic, slim, full, all) for progressive feature loading",
    "Retina display support and reduced motion accessibility",
    "Particle interactions: attract, repulse, bubble, grab, push, remove, and more",
    "Multiple path algorithms: Perlin noise, Simplex noise, curl noise, SVG paths, and more"
  ],
